	* src/libYARP_dev/src/TestFrameGrabber.cpp: simplify testing
	the IPreciselyTimed interface by making the timestamps of
	test frames be "coincidentally" NNN.NNN42 - if these timestamps
	ever get replaced by network transmission timestamps, this
	should now be obvious.

