	* conf/YarpSystemCheck.cmake: add experimental SKIP_ACE option
	to compile YARP without using ACE.  Support for some features
	is dropped, and only Linux is targeted.  This draws on
	Anne van Rossum's yarp-lightweight fork at 
	https://dev.almende.com/svn/yarp-lightweight
	[thanks Anne van Rossum].

