2010-07-23  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@debian.humanoids.iit.it>

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/Property.cpp: support multi-line lists
	in config files without requiring "\" at the end of lines.
	So:
	   mymatrix ((1 2 3)
	             (4 5 6)
	             (7 8 9))
	will work as expected.  Successive lines are appended until
	all parentheses and quotes are balanced.

