	consistency.  Provides ACE_FOUND, ACE_LIBRARIES, ACE_INCLUDE_DIRS.

	* conf/FindOpenCV.cmake: freshen OpenCV search script.
	Provides OpenCV_FOUND, OpenCV_LIBRARIES, OpenCV_INCLUDE_DIRS.

