2010-01-27  Ugo Pattacini  <ugo.pattacini@iit.it>

	* src/libYARP_dev/src/RemoteControlBoard.cpp:
    timeout handling bug fix

2010-01-27  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/Companion.cpp: added "yarp quiet" option,
	e.g. "yarp quiet read /read".  This is the opposite of the
	existing "yarp verbose" option.  The effect is the same as
	setting the YARP_QUIET environment variable.

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/Network.cpp: added "YARP_QUIET" environment
	variable.  If set to 1, no messages should be emitted by YARP.
	Note to developers - please use YARP_ERROR/YARP_DEBUG/YARP_INFO
	macros for all messages so that users can control their
	appearance.

