2009-11-20  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* conf/UsePkgConfig.cmake: use "modern" (>= cmake 2.4) pkg-config
	tests when available.

	* conf/YarpModuleHooks.cmake: merge libYARP_dev material into
	yarpmod when devices are to be loaded automatically.  Otherwise
	there is a circular dependency between libYARP_dev and yarpmod
	that causes occasional problems.

