	for include syntax.

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/Property.cpp: fix tagged includes (the syntax
	[include TAG "filename.ini"] was not doing what it should have).
	[Thanks Christian Wressnegger] for reporting this!

2009-11-13  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@nominal.csail.mit.edu>

