	* src/libYARP_OS/src/NameConfig.cpp: check for HOMEPATH before
	HOME when looking for config files, in order to give consistent
	behavior on windows.

2009-08-12  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/yarpserver/: initial checkin of new yarp server version,
	"yarpserver3".  This is not yet the default server, and won't be
	for a while.

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/ResourceFinder.cpp: allow for multiple
	fallback directories (default_capability) in the resource finder
	policy file.

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/ResourceFinder.cpp: give ultimate priority
	over config settings to the command line in all circumstances
	(thanks David Vernon).

	* src/libYARP_OS/harness/ResourceFinderTest.cpp: regression test
	to make sure command line can override config files for config
	settings.
	
