	inadvertently hidden Searchable::check() methods.
	[thanks Jonas Ruesch] for pointing out problem.

2009-07-23  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/Bottle.cpp: remove incorrect return on
	void method [thanks David Vernon]

2009-07-21  Arjan Gijsberts  <arjan@liralab.it>

	* src/libYARP_math/src/math.cpp
	* src/libYARP_math/include/yarp/math/Math.h
	* src/libYARP_math/harness/MathTest.cpp
	Added 'luinv' function for square matrix inversion using LU 
	decomposition.
	Added 'chinv' function for positive definite matrix inversion using 
	Cholesky decomposition. This function depends on GSL 1.12 and is 
	commented out until this version is installed on most target machines.

2009-07-07 Lorenzo Natale <nat@robotcub.org>
	* src/libYARP_dev/src/include/yarp/dev/ControlBoardInterfaces.h
        * src/libYARP_dev/dev/src/RemoteControlBoard.cpp:
	cleaned code and added IControlMode interface, ITorqueControl
        IControlModeRaw, ITorqueControlRaw

2009-07-03  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/PortCore.cpp: fix administration interface
	bug when listing inputs and outputs - access to the connections
	wasn't thread-safe, and could fail if connections were
	simultaneously added/removed.  [Thanks Alejandro R. Mosteo] for
	bug report #2801261.

2009-07-01  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/include/yarp/os/impl/BottleImpl.h: fix
	for blob copy bug, #2815097 submitted by Alejandro R. Mosteo

	* src/libYARP_OS/harness/BottleTest.cpp: added regression
	test for blobs with internal nulls, based on bug
	#2815097, thanks [Alejandro R. Mosteo]

2009-06-30  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_sig/src/ImageCopy.cpp: small patch to deal 
	correctly with PixelMono16 type on big-endian systems.
	[Thanks Giovanni Saponaro] for testing on Mac OSX (PPC).

2009-06-29  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/doc/cmd_yarp.dox: update documentation for yarp 
	companion program for commands "yarp where/detect/conf".

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/Companion.cpp: add "yarp detect" command
	to scan for nameserver in a controlled way, and give
	debugging tips for when problems arise.

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/NameClient.cpp: stop ports from 
	automatically scanning for nameserver if they cannot find it.

