	allow reuse of fallback multicast name server

2009-06-23  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/BottleImpl.cpp: fix bug in smartAdd() method 
	that failed to correctly interpret sequences with multiple periods
	as strings (e.g. IP addresses).

	* src/libYARP_OS/harness/BottleTest.cpp: add test for correct
	interpretation of IPv4 addresses as strings.
		

2009-06-17  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/harness/PortReaderBufferTest.cpp: mistake
	in test: messages in checkCallback need to be send with "strict"
	flag set, to be sure they don't get dropped.
	[Thanks Alejandro R. Mosteo] for drawing attention to 
	PortReaderBufferTest problem.

	* src/libYARP_OS/include/yarp/os/impl/McastCarrier.h: allocate
	global mcast election object only if mcast is actually used.
	ACE's hash objects are quite large!

2009-06-15  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_sig/src/Vector.cpp: improve read() method to 
	do a sanity check, for better error recovery [thanks Arjan Gijsberts]

