	* src/libYARP_OS/harness/PortReaderBufferTest.cpp: increase
	timeout for callback test, it may be too tight.

2009-06-12  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* example/swig/: lots of updates to make Java examples work again
	after yarp classes were moved into a package 
	[thanks Sebastian Wrede]

2009-06-09  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/include/yarp/os/impl/ThreadImpl.h: avoid using
	ACE_Auto_Event class, in favor of Semaphores - just because they
	have been more tested against different ACE builds.  
	[Thanks Alejandro R. Mosteo] for drawing attention to ThreadTest
	problems in bug report #2801261

	* src/libYARP_OS/harness/ThreadTest.cpp: regression test for
	isRunning() was not quite right, it could fail even for 
	correct behavior.  Thanks to Alejandro R. Mosteo for drawing
	attention to ThreadTest problems in bug report #2801261

