	Gianluca for pointing out this was not happening.

2009-03-04  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* conf/YarpOptions.cmake: add an option to replace ACE-based
	implementation of yarp::os::impl::String with a std::string
	typedef. This is useful for some debugging I'm doing, and is
	an option we had often talked about adding in the past.

