	on a connection that has not yet been opened.

2008-09-16  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/include/yarp/Protocol.h: fix expectIndex; it
	doesn't behave well when the underlying carrier has a transient
	(as opposed to critical) failure.  This may be contributing to
	problems seen with multicast transmission (see bug 2102263 on
	sourceforge YARP page)

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/ResourceFinder.cpp: fix problem
	with configuration options getting lost.  Add path
	for default config file to search path.


	* src/libYARP_OS/include/yarp/os/ResourceFinder.h: add
	setDefaultConfigFile method, to specify a default for
	--from.

