	* src/libYARP_OS/src/BottleImpl.cpp: stop the character
	sequence "." from being interpreted as a number.

	* src/libYARP_OS/harness/ResourceFinderTest.cpp: start adding
	regression tests for ResourceFinder

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/ResourceFinder.cpp: implement "--from config.ini"
	for loading settings into ResourceFinder from a file.  This is
	like the "--file config.ini" behavior of the Module class and
	yarpdev etc.  The names are inconsistent for complicated reasons.

	* src/libYARP_OS/include/yarp/os/ResourceFinder.h: make ResourceFinder
	a regular "Searchable" so that methods like findGroup work.


