	* src/doc/yarp_without_yarp.dox: tutorial on communicating
	with YARP Ports without actually using YARP.

	* src/doc/name_server.dox: update the name server documentation.

	* src/doc/using_cmake.dox: add a more extensive cmake tutorial.

2008-07-09  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/doc/dox_header.html: bring back search box in online
	documentation

2008-07-08  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* conf/YarpVersion.cmake: froze version 2.2.1.

2008-07-02  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/modules/ffmpeg/ffmpeg_api.cpp: fixed bug remapping formats
	using newer ffmpeg libraries, oops.

2008-07-02  Giacomo Spigler  <spiglerg@gmail.com>

	* src/modules/cuda/CUDADeviceDriver.cpp: Little modification to 
	add CUDA 2.0 (beta) compatibility.

2008-06-30  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/Terminator.cpp: Terminators are strange
	entities.  They tell the name server that they are ports, but
	don't obey any port protocols. they accept the string "quit", and
	that is all.  I've now changed them to also accept "CONNECT
	foo\nd\nquit\n" in preparation for replacing them with real ports
	in a later version of YARP.

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/ResourceFinder.cpp: basic implementation
	of policy for finding configuration files.

	* src/libYARP_OS/include/yarp/os/ResourceFinder.h: stub for 
	tool for helping find configuration files.

	* src/libYARP_dev/include/yarp/dev/ControlBoardInterfacesImpl.h: 
	adding missing copyright/license statement.

2008-06-27  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/harness/NetTypeTest.cpp: add regression
	test for NetInt16.

	* src/libYARP_sig/src/ImageCopy.cpp: set up mapping from
	PixelMono16 to all other pixel types, for efficient image
	copies.

	* src/libYARP_sig/src/Image.cpp: apply patch 
	[thanks Stefan Freyr Stefansson] for PixelMono16 type

	* src/libYARP_sig/include/yarp/sig/Image.h: apply patch from
	Stefan Freyr Stefansson for PixelMono16 type, replacing uint_16
	type with NetUint16.

	* src/libYARP_OS/include/yarp/os/NetInt32.h: add implementations
	of little-endian 16-bit signed integers, and 16/32-bit unsigned
	integers, for use on big-endian systems as NetInt16, NetUint16, and
	NetUint32 respectively.  On little-endian systems these map
	to native types instead.

	* conf/YarpReqLib.cmake: get CMake to check for size of 16-bit 
	integers (needed for portable PixelMono16 type for images).

2008-06-26  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* conf/DEVICEConfig.cmake.in: deal better with debug-mode library 
	dependencies for module libraries.

	* src/libYARP_sig/src/Image.cpp: make default IPL type for unknown 
	16-bit types be unsigned - more likely.

2008-06-25  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* conf/YARPConfig.cmake.in: debug-mode device dependencies weren't
	being propagated in MSVC with CMake 2.6

	* CMakeLists.txt: add some policy flags to make CMake 2.6 happy.

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/NameServer.cpp: deprecate server-side
	"yarp name gc" in favor of "yarp clean".

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/Companion.cpp: add "yarp clean" command,
	a client-side replacement for the server-side "yarp name gc"
	command.  Both commands ping all listed ports and unregister
	those that are no longer active.

	* src/libYARP_OS/include/yarp/os/Contact.h: add constructor
	so Contacts can be configured from Property/Bottles.  Makes
	it easier to interpret port information sent from name server.

2008-06-18  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/PortCore.cpp: protect against a potential
	collision on a packet reference count.

2008-06-18  Alessandro Scalzo <alessandro@liralab.it>
	* src/yarp/libYARP_dev/include/yarp/dev/DataSource.h : modified
	* src/yarp/libYARP_dev/include/yarp/dev/ServerFrameGrabber.h : modified
	* src/yarp/libYARP_dev/src/ServerFrameGrabber.cpp : modified
	IPreciselyTimed interface added. Implemented in DragonflyDeviceDriver
	in order to provide precise acquisition Stamp.

2008-06-17  Paul Fitzpatrick  <paulfitz@alum.mit.edu>

	* src/yarpdev/yarpdev.cpp: Fix failure on autoconf builds.

	* src/libYARP_OS/src/NameServer.cpp: multithread the name-server
	so communication delays with one client do not affect others.
	Of course, operations on the name database remain atomic.

