	* src/libYARP_OS/src/BottleImpl.cpp: temporary Bottle-specific
	fix for bug 1982162 ("connection lost between one output and
	two inputs")

2008-06-05  Lorenzo Natale  <nat@liralab.it>
	* src/libYARP_dev/src/RemoteControlBoard.cpp
	* src/libYARP_dev/src/ServerControlBoard.cpp
	* src/libYARP_dev/include/yarp/dev/ControlBoardHelpers.h:
	ServerControlBoard and RemoteControlBoard classes are now
	in separate files. Code is still quite messy, but improving.

	RemoteControlBoard::getEncoders is now non blocking. This prevents
	clients from getting stuck when server dies.
	
