	accidental copies of BufferedPort.  Closes bug 1968646.

	* src/libYARP_dev/include/yarp/dev/PolyDriver.h: added private
	copy constructor / assignment operators to catch accidental
	copies.  PolyDriver objects cannot be copied. 
	Closes bug 1968253.

